author: IGN
description:
Check out a clip from Digimon Beatbreak featuring a digivolution! Digimon Beatbreak is coming to Hulu and Crunchyroll this fall season!

Tomoro Tenma lives in a world where human thoughts and emotions—known as “e-Pulse”—power AI devices called Sapotama. But when Digimon begin materializing from Sapotama and feeding on e-Pulse, society begins to fracture. After Gekkomon appears from his device, Tomoro joins Glowing Dawn, a secret team investigating rogue Digimon and the dark truth of a system both fueled and corrupted by emotion.

#IGN #Anime #Digimon
title: Digimon Beatbreak - Official Clip (English Subtitles)

author: IGN
description: Don't miss the Launch Trailer for Megabonk, a third-person bullet hell action roguelike developed by Vedinad. Players will fight through waves of endless enemies to grab loot, upgrade weapons, unlock characters, and level up from run to run to create new builds with dynamic effects. Megabonk is available now for PC (Steam).
title: Megabonk - Official Launch Trailer

author: IGN
description:
Microsoft has announced a major Xbox Game Pass price increase, raising the cost of its subscription service across multiple tiers. In this episode, we break down what the new pricing looks like, how it compares to other platforms, and whether Game Pass is still the best deal in gaming.
